result.title: Denial of judgement error on codeforces
result.content: Hey guys, when I submitted a solution to problem (603A-Alternative Thinking) , an error occurred called Denial of judgement . So, what is Denial of Judgement error and why is it occurring? Can someone enlighten me on this issue? Here the link to my solution-http://codeforces.com/contest/603/submission/35550623
